            <title><![CDATA[习近平高铁抵港：香港浴火重生 一国两制有强大生命力]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/5_0.JPG?VersionId=vKfrc9bK.RGQeEo1V_Rk5Wv679qk5_nX&amp;itok=S7iwJZiz" alt="" data-caption="中国国家主席习近平（右）周四下午乘高铁专列抵达香港，夫人彭丽媛（左）随行。（视频截图）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/5_0.JPG?VersionId=vKfrc9bK.RGQeEo1V_Rk5Wv679qk5_nX&amp;itok=S7iwJZiz" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
